Text: One of the funniest films I've ever seen.
May be funny but if it isn't seeded no-one else will know will they. I despair sometimes. )o:

Kan inte någon seeda denna? Snääääääälla!!!!!
Jag såg den när den var ny, och det är en av de konstigaste filmer jag sett. Bra? Hmm, kanske det... Sevärd iallafall!

Thanks Xtrovaganza....this is one of many older "B" movies I have on Beta tape that I've been looking for on DVD (or divx), to save me the time of capping from the original Beta tapes...will seed this for a while in appreciation of this rare (and yes, ridiculously funny) film.
